Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.56,0:00:32.86,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Seiji-kun...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.33,0:00:43.53,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}É você o líder dos Dekarutos?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.85,0:00:48.57,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Você é o Cão Raivoso...\n Cão Raivoso Sawamura, não é?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.70,0:00:51.10,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Meu colega...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.29,0:00:53.69,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Parece que vocês realmente cuidaram dele.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.06,0:00:59.05,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Retribuirei vocês por isso.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.07,0:01:05.41,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Com minha Mão Direita do Demônio!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.69,0:01:10.74,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sawamura!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.47,0:01:24.47,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Incrível!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.66,0:01:28.06,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Era o que eu esperava do Sawamura-san!\n Eu realmente agradeço!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.57,0:01:32.59,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Da próxima vez que você pedir por minha ajuda,\n dê-me adversários que valham a pena.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.98,0:01:35.37,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não é um hábito meu atormentar caras fracos.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.64,0:01:39.14,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Muito obrigado!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.00,0:01:46.35,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ahn... Você
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.39,0:01:50.59,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}P-Por favor, saía comigo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.85,0:01:52.08,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Por favor!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.98,0:01:54.53,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}M-Me Desculpe...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.78,0:01:58.12,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu já... gosto de alguém...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.66,0:02:10.33,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}{\i1\c&HFF&}Fora!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.05,0:02:11.65,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}{\i1\c&HFF&}Fora!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.82,0:02:12.45,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Merda!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.51,0:02:13.00,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}{\i1\c&HFF&}Fora!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.05,0:02:15.85,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Strike! Você está fora!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.08,0:02:20.85,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}O jogo acabou, é a 21ª derrota dos Marine Stars. Uma seqüencia de 21 derrotas!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.98,0:02:23.45,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Cale a boca! Ainda são somente 20!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.78,0:02:26.76,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Por favor, assista Ultra Marin a essa hora na próxima semana.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.61,0:02:29.56,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu sou Sawamura Seiji.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.26,0:02:32.73,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}17 anos e 2 meses sem uma namorada.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.30,0:02:35.24,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu tenho um recorde de 20 corações quebrados,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.39,0:02:37.77,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}e continua aumentando.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.62,0:02:40.61,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Outra porção grande!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.18,0:02:51.82,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Calem a boca!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.94,0:02:55.42,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Vocês parem de namorar perto de mim!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.79,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Nossa, esses caras...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.65,0:03:07.29,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Onii-chan!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.86,0:03:10.11,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Pare de me chamar de "onii-chan".
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.19,0:03:12.05,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Você arranjou uma namorada?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.02,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Cala a boca!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.06,0:03:13.96,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Se manda.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.80,0:03:17.31,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Talvez eu devesse ser sua namorada?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.47,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Isso não é da sua conta!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.71,0:03:21.11,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Bye bye!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.28,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Vazio...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.50,0:03:26.56,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sinto-me tão vazio!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.42,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu apenas queria ter uma namorada normal
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.55,0:03:34.24,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}e ter uma vida escolar normal, equilibrada, brilhante e feliz.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.77,0:03:38.76,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}É sem sentido ser forte em brigas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.77,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Por causa de todos esse caras com medo de mim as garotas também ficam...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.31,0:03:45.87,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Vou continuar azarado pelos meus três anos de colegial,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.90,0:03:48.20,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}terminando sem namorada, e com minha mão direita como amante.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.53,0:03:50.44,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Uma adolescência negra como essa é muita crueldade!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.31,0:03:53.46,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Por favor, saía comigo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.82,0:03:54.95,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Me desculpe...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.53,0:03:58.72,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu já tenho alguém de quem gosto...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.25,0:04:01.68,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Vamos continuar somente como amigos...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.41,0:04:04.81,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sinto muito...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.39,0:04:18.09,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não importa quem! Mas por favor, seja minha namorada!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.31,0:04:19.06,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Verdade?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.02,0:04:24.82,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Q-quem falou isso?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.72,0:04:32.49,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Foi você?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.90,0:04:44.35,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Devo ter me machucado seriamente para estar ouvindo coisas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.92,0:04:47.71,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}De novo, uma voz de menina!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.55,0:04:53.60,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}A voz está ficando mais alta?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.23,0:04:54.66,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.08,0:04:56.23,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Es-Estou me sentindo tonta...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.17,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Preciso de uma aspirina!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.14,0:05:07.92,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Fique calmo! Acalme-se, Sawamura Seiji.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.88,0:05:15.44,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Está frio! Está frio! Está frio!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.77,0:05:20.57,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}O que está havendo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.06,0:05:33.91,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ei! O que é isso?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.56,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}O-O que é você?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.64,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Por que tem uma garota na manga da minha camiseta?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.07,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}É o Seiji-kun!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.13,0:07:21.65,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}E não é um sonho!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.72,0:07:24.63,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}É o Seiji-kun! É o Seiji-kun!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.63,0:07:25.44,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}O que?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.63,0:07:34.13,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.02,0:07:39.34,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não! Não! Não!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.80,0:07:41.59,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não olhe!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.70,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Por que estou na mão de Seiji-kun?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.33,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}É o que eu quero saber!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.33,0:07:50.97,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Por que há seios em minha mão direita?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.05,0:07:53.10,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não. Por que minha mão direita se tornou uma garota?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.25,0:07:56.03,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu também não sei o porque.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.57,0:07:59.17,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Cale-se, como você sabe quem sou eu?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.50,0:08:01.25,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Bem...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.35,0:08:03.40,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.30,0:08:08.20,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu sempre tive uma quedinha por você!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.34,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Quedinha?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.38,0:08:14.62,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu tenho amado você desde que o vi pela primeira vez à três anos atrás.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.17,0:08:19.00,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Pensei que seria maravilhoso se pudéssemos estar juntos.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.23,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Isto é uma confissão.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.51,0:08:25.80,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Essa é a primeira vez que alguém se confessa para mim.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.52,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não, não posso ficar feliz de jeito algum.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.91,0:08:34.07,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não posso ficar feliz quando minha mão direita se confessa a mim.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.05,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Vo-Você...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.52,0:08:38.32,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sim?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.53,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu não sei se é amor ou não,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.35,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}isso me incomoda!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.51,0:08:46.31,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Com um braço desse jeito, como vou poder viver a minha vida?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.75,0:08:50.12,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Mas... mesmo que você diga isso...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.98,0:08:54.52,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Para mim também, eu acordei e tinha me tornado a mão direita de Seiji-kun.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.96,0:08:56.46,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sem saber porque...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.24,0:09:00.22,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}foi realmente assustador, o suficiente para me fazer chorar.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.51,0:09:03.10,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Mas...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.05,0:09:06.72,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}para ser capaz de ficar com o meu querido Seiji-kun,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.89,0:09:09.96,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}eu estou bem feliz... assim.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.52,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Nada de "hehehe", viu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.58,0:09:15.46,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu não estou nem um pouco feliz com isso!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.60,0:09:20.79,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sabe, eu sou o garoto temido que chamam de Cão Raivoso Sawamura!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.82,0:09:22.04,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Para alguém como eu...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.16,0:09:25.04,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Venha, eu te matarei!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.07,0:09:26.19,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Matar!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.31,0:09:28.66,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Isso faria eu parecer não muito legal!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.79,0:09:31.79,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu farei o meu melhor para parecer legal!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.09,0:09:35.59,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não, não é isso que quero dizer...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.85,0:09:37.98,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Droga, o que devo fazer?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.17,0:09:41.85,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Falando nisso, o que aconteceu com seu corpo original?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.61,0:09:47.77,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Você deveria deixar todas as suas revistas em um só lugar.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.04,0:09:50.71,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Agora estou separando as novas revistas das que são lixos.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.14,0:09:53.99,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}O que você está fazendo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.02,0:09:57.50,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Estava um pouquinho bagunçado, então resolvi dar uma ajeitada.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.01,0:10:07.64,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Algo assim pode não ser tão ruim.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.07,0:10:13.34,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Mi-Miruku-chan!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.36,0:10:14.86,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Debaixo da cama também!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.54,0:10:17.37,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Pare! Pare com isso!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.07,0:10:20.51,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não pegue isso!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.90,0:10:24.38,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Vamos jogar isso fora, agora!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.14,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não decida isso por conta própria!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.88,0:10:28.98,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não se preocupe com isso, onde fica sua casa?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.00,0:10:29.95,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Mi-Minha casa?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.17,0:10:32.21,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sim, se nós formos onde você mora,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.49,0:10:35.07,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}nós podemos descobrir porque você ficou assim.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.76,0:10:36.46,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Mas...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.98,0:10:38.97,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Você não quer voltar ao normal?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.39,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Você não quer ficar desse jeito?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.89,0:10:43.06,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Claro que não!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.30,0:10:51.20,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sawamura-san! Obrigado por ontem!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.77,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Onde está o Sawamura-san?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.60,0:10:55.38,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ele faltou.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.98,0:10:56.79,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Faltou?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.27,0:10:58.81,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ocupado brigando, provavelmente.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.20,0:11:02.16,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Como o delinqüente não está aqui, hoje está um dia tranquilo e agrádavel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.33,0:11:03.21,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}O que você disse?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.47,0:11:04.07,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Que foi...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.36,0:11:05.79,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Que Sawamura-san...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.06,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ei, Representante.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.84,0:11:10.36,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Vá pegar algumas cópias para mim no almoxarifado.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.74,0:11:11.29,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sim!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.97,0:11:15.87,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Que garota atrevida.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.46,0:11:17.84,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Marin-chan...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.30,0:11:29.99,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Midori... Midori!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.49,0:11:37.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAnime Ace\fs28\c&HC08000&\a6}Kasugano
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.75,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Es-Essa é sua casa?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.46,0:11:41.18,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sim.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.93,0:11:51.10,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}In... In... Incrível!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.65,0:11:53.84,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sério?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.80,0:11:57.38,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Você realmente é algum tipo de princesa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.56,0:11:58.41,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Bem...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.40,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Vamos voltar.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.85,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Estou bem desse jeito...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.91,0:12:04.57,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não é bom!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.98,0:12:09.52,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sim?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.96,0:12:14.29,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Hum, eu sou amigo de sua filha...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.77,0:12:18.63,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ela saiu devido a assuntos inesperados.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.15,0:12:20.15,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Assuntos inesperados?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.71,0:12:23.14,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu não acho que ela vá voltar hoje,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.98,0:12:25.56,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Saiu, você disse... Para onde?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.13,0:12:26.97,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Por favor, vá embora.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.13,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}E-Ei!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.01,0:12:33.46,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sawamura-san pode ter pego um resfriado ou algo parecido?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.35,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Talvez eu deva ir visitá-lo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.30,0:12:38.78,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Hum, desculpe-me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.12,0:12:41.33,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Você é o Miyahara-san?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.13,0:12:50.40,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ga-Garotas da Escola Feminina Kamunegi...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.72,0:12:52.45,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Vocês precisam de mim para alguma coisa?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.57,0:12:57.13,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Hum, nós somos fãs de Sawamura-san.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.53,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Fãs de Sawamura-san?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.58,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}O que significa isso?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.95,0:13:09.45,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Você está aqui, mas há uma outra de você lá fora?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.92,0:13:13.87,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Isso é ruim.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.99,0:13:15.01,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Muito ruim.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.89,0:13:18.29,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Mas estou feliz agora.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.89,0:13:22.38,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Porque eu posso ficar com o meu querido Seiji-kun.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.36,0:13:29.69,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu sempre ficava olhando você da plataforma.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.03,0:13:34.33,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Mas eu sempre olhava você à distância...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.71,0:13:58.60,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu sou aluna da Escola Secundária Ogurabashi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.07,0:14:01.61,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Você não é apenas rica, mas também é da elite?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.07,0:14:07.86,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Todos os meus amigos o conhecem como o delinqüente da Escola Secundária Sakuradamon e têm medo de você.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.52,0:14:09.90,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Mas eu sei...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.17,0:14:12.13,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}que você realmente é uma boa pessoa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.51,0:14:16.44,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Você sempre salva os mais fracos.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.72,0:14:18.95,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu realmente gosto disso em você, Seiji-kun.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.04,0:14:20.69,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Por isso...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.13,0:14:24.12,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}agora estou bastante feliz.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.08,0:14:37.03,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Alô.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.05,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Obrigado por ontem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.86,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}O que aconteceu hoje?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.15,0:14:43.82,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ah... Eu peguei um resfriado.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.92,0:14:47.26,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Então era só um resfriado, afinal?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.30,0:14:48.71,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Isso é terrível!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.02,0:14:50.38,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Vamos visitá-lo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.09,0:14:53.64,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sawamura-san. Nós vamos até aí para visitá-lo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.85,0:14:56.32,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não, não é nada, não se preocupe.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.90,0:15:00.37,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}De fato, suas fãs estão aqui comigo agora mesmo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.66,0:15:04.07,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Elas estão dizendo que querem visitá-lo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.74,0:15:07.74,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Realmente?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.06,0:15:09.35,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Então não posso fazer nada.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.97,0:15:13.92,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Seiji-kun?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.02,0:15:21.54,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Legal!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.03,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ouça com cuidado! Entendeu?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.66,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não importa o quanto você goste de mim,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.66,0:15:47.35,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}não tem como eu gostar de você, sendo você a  minha mão direita!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.35,0:15:48.30,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}De fato, é doentio!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.90,0:15:51.06,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}O que eu quero é uma namorada humana,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.18,0:15:53.15,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}não uma namorada de mão-direita!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.98,0:16:00.72,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não faça nenhum som. Entendeu?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.36,0:16:06.17,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não toque tantas ve...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.03,0:16:08.15,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Legal o conhecer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.44,0:16:09.58,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sou a Youko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.98,0:16:11.21,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}E eu sou a Yuka.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.31,0:16:14.28,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}{\i1}Legal!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.28,0:16:18.19,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}{\i1}Strike!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.09,0:16:20.54,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Oi, eu sou o Sawamura.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.83,0:16:22.76,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Como está seu resfriado?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.97,0:16:24.10,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sem problemas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.34,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Que bom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.58,0:16:26.53,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Onde está o Miya?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.76,0:16:28.53,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ele disse que estava indo buscar alguns salgadinhos na loja de conveniência.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.76,0:16:29.21,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sério?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.65,0:16:30.48,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Bem, entrem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.77,0:16:36.02,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sério? Seus pais vivem no exterior?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.17,0:16:40.60,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu tenho uma irmã mais velha, mas ela mora com o namorado e raramente vem para casa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.63,0:16:42.99,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Então, talvez nós pudessemos cozinhar para você na próxima vez.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.82,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Algo cheio de amor para Sawamura-san.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.09,0:16:48.48,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Rolinhos Primavera, por favor coma!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.51,0:16:55.01,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}{\i1}Legal! Rolinhos Primavera!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.35,0:16:57.44,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sim, estou ansioso para comê-los.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.97,0:17:00.87,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Hum... Onde é o toalete?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.09,0:17:03.76,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}No final do corredor, a sua direita.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.20,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Com licença.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.27,0:17:11.25,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Miya está atrasado.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.50,0:17:13.69,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sawamura-san...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.02,0:17:14.56,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}O que foi?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.06,0:17:19.81,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sawamura-san, você gosta... de meninas mais jovens?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.93,0:17:23.92,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Porque não parece que agora você tenha uma namorada.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.74,0:17:27.53,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Se sou boa o bastante para você...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.19,0:17:31.27,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}{\i1}Legal!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.08,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}{\i1}Chegou! Chegou!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.08,0:17:39.78,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}{\i1}Depois de 17 anos e 2 meses, a primavera finalmente chegou!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.08,0:17:44.12,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu já namorei vinte garotas mais novas do que eu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.09,0:17:46.05,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sawamura-san.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.87,0:17:51.75,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ahn... Você pode me beijar?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.92,0:17:58.88,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ela é tão audaciosa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.74,0:18:00.75,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}É embaraçoso...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.67,0:18:02.86,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Feche seus olhos.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.93,0:18:24.33,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sawamura!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.32,0:18:26.60,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Morra!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.85,0:18:28.65,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}O que?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.97,0:18:37.03,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Parece que você percebeu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.90,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Nós somos do Dekaruto.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.94,0:18:42.07,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Nós vamos nos vingar por você ter hospitalizado nossos namorados.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.42,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ei, aguente firme!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.75,0:18:45.12,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ei!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.86,0:18:47.43,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Que droga!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.57,0:18:48.93,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Que droga! Que droga! Que droga!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.30,0:18:51.04,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Isso não quer sair!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.28,0:18:52.56,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ei!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.58,0:18:54.21,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Você não nos ouviu?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.27,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Venha, Sawamura!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.73,0:18:58.39,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Saiam da frente!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.60,0:19:03.08,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Agora você conseguiu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.30,0:19:08.42,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não tenho escolha.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.49,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Cortarei com isso aqui...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.56,0:19:11.57,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu devo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.64,0:19:21.95,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sentimos muito! Por favor poupe nossas vidas!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.97,0:19:25.27,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ei?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.18,0:19:26.53,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ei!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.08,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Você não está morta, certo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.50,0:19:29.87,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ei!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.45,0:19:35.37,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Seiji-kun?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.97,0:19:36.67,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Você está bem?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.77,0:19:40.19,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Você está bem, Seiji-kun?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.46,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Se machucou?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.50,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu estou bem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.27,0:19:46.35,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Que bom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.60,0:19:49.65,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Desmaiei.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.84,0:19:53.32,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Mas eu mantive nossa promessa, né?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.18,0:19:54.93,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Promessa?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.01,0:19:58.63,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,Eu...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.68,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu não fiz um som.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.04,0:20:06.79,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu... sempre tive essa quedinha por você!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.23,0:20:11.98,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Por favor... me diga seu nome.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.34,0:20:14.36,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Midori.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.84,0:20:16.71,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Kasugano Midori.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.57,0:20:18.58,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Diga, Midori.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.14,0:20:24.06,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}De agora em diante, você pode quebrar nossa promessa em situações como essa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.43,0:20:26.21,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Você pode me dizer com sua voz.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.31,0:20:29.76,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Mas... as pessoas me descobrirão.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.16,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu não ligo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.34,0:20:32.29,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Nos preocuparemos quando isso acontecer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.64,0:20:36.64,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Não é um segredo grande o bastante para justificar que uma garota se machuque.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.26,0:20:39.28,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Mesmo que você tenha se tornado minha mão direita,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.79,0:20:42.43,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}você ainda é uma garota.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.26,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Seiji-kun...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.58,0:20:50.66,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Eu te amo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.44,0:20:56.42,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Sawamura-san, você está bem?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.53,0:20:57.94,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}As garotas...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.58,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Solte! Pare!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.60,0:21:03.68,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}O que você está fazendo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.68,0:21:19.94,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Para poder estar assim junto de meu querido Seiji-kun,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.18,0:21:22.09,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}é como um sonho, mesmo agora.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.17,0:21:27.44,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Ser sua mão direita ao invés de sua namorada é um pouco frustrante.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.14,0:21:31.97,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Mas é um segredo compartilhado somente por nós dois nesse mundo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.61,0:21:35.10,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Quando penso dessa maneira, eu realmente fico feliz
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.52,0:21:44.36,MnH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(15,50)}Nessa noite, foi a primeira vez na qual vi a lua do quarto do Seiji, foi muito bonito.
